          ]
        }
      ],
      "comparison_table": [
        "✅ already → جملة مثبتة (I have already done it.)",
        "✅ yet → نفي أو سؤال (I haven't done it yet / Have you done it yet?)",
        "✅ just → حدث قريب جداً (I have just done it.)",
        "✅ since → نقطة بداية (since Monday / since 2020)",
        "✅ for → فترة زمنية (for two hours / for a week)"
